org.melior.client.web.rest

Class RestClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.client.core.ClientConfig
      • org.melior.client.web.rest.RestClientConfig
        • org.melior.client.web.rest.RestClient

  • public class RestClient
extends RestClientConfig
    Implements an easy to use, auto-configuring HTTP REST client with connection pooling, automatic object mapping and fast secure HTTP connections.

    The client writes timing details to the logs while dispatching HTTP requests to the HTTP end-point. The client automatically converts any exception that occurs during communication with the HTTP end-point into a standard RemotingException.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Melior
